    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Canvas》中创作惊艳画作，赢取丝带荣誉——这款备受赞誉的桌游现已推出数字版，考验你的策略与艺术眼光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209240/extras/af035c767fdc81e090510a80963dbeca.poster.avif?t=1761582551\" width=1080 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209240/extras/af035c767fdc81e090510a80963dbeca.webm?t=1761582551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209240/extras/af035c767fdc81e090510a80963dbeca.mp4?t=1761582551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Canvas》中，你将组合透明的艺术卡牌，创作出独一无二的画作。每张卡牌不仅增添画面元素，还带有影响得分的图标。如何层叠卡牌、遮挡或展示哪些图标，是赢取得分条件、获得丝带的关键。每幅画都将计入总分，同时成为一件独特的艺术作品，并自动生成个性化标题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209240/extras/c56fe1835f87cf565fee87af34748ea6.poster.avif?t=1761582551\" width=1080 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209240/extras/c56fe1835f87cf565fee87af34748ea6.webm?t=1761582551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209240/extras/c56fe1835f87cf565fee87af34748ea6.mp4?t=1761582551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张卡牌都绘有令人惊叹的艺术画面，激发你的创意灵感。无论是新手玩家还是资深策略家，都能在游戏中找到充实的挑战与乐趣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨平台在线对战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友创建私人线上游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地多人游戏（同一设备或通过 Steam Remote Play）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人模式可对抗 AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多设备同步进度：在一台设备上开始，换设备无缝继续</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收藏你的最佳画作，尽览个人画廊</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >互动式教学引导，轻松上手</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整艺术卡牌集，带来无限画作组合可能</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >© 2025 Mipmap，经由 Tycoon Games 授权发行</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209240/extras/7ae8eb86b6216117cd94daee17bf155f.avif?t=1761582551\" width=1560 height=274 /></span></p>",
